flowchart TD
    Start([User opens ResearchMind]) --> Home{Choose Mode}

    Home -->|Mode 1| DD[Deep Dive]
    Home -->|Mode 2| TM[Topic Mastery]

    %% ---------- MODE 1: DEEP DIVE ----------
    DD --> Input1[/Paste paper title or arXiv link/]
    Input1 --> Scrape1[Scraper Agent<br/>pdfplumber + BeautifulSoup]
    Scrape1 --> Explain[Explainer Agent<br/>GPT-4o breakdown]
    Explain --> Sections[Section-by-section explainer<br/>mastered terms highlighted]
    Sections --> Chat[3-Mode Chat<br/>Standard / Socratic / Devil's Advocate]
    Chat --> Export

    %% ---------- MODE 2: TOPIC MASTERY ----------
    TM --> Input2[/Enter a topic/]
    Input2 --> Diag[Diagnostic Agent<br/>5-question calibration]
    Diag --> Disc[Discovery Agent<br/>finds relevant papers]
    Disc --> Graph[Graph Builder Agent<br/>builds knowledge graph]
    Graph --> Scrape2[Scraper Agent<br/>fetches prerequisites]
    Scrape2 --> QuizGen[Quiz Gen Agent<br/>GPT-4o questions]

    QuizGen --> KG[Interactive Knowledge Graph<br/>mastered vs. pending concepts]
    KG --> CQ{Confidence Quiz<br/>70% pass gate?}
    CQ -->|Fail| Prereq[Prerequisites Panel<br/>YouTube + key concepts]
    Prereq --> KG
    CQ -->|Pass| SR[Spaced Repetition<br/>review scheduling]
    SR --> Export

    %% ---------- SHARED OUTPUT ----------
    Export[PDF Export<br/>full session compiled]
    Export --> End([Mastery achieved])

    %% ---------- INFRA NOTE ----------
    subgraph Backend [Backend: FastAPI + LangGraph orchestration]
        Diag
        Disc
        Graph
        Scrape2
        QuizGen
    end

    Qdrant[(Qdrant<br/>vector search)] -.retrieval.- Backend
    SSE[/Live progress streamed via SSE/] -.real-time updates.- Backend

    %% ---------- STYLING ----------
    classDef mode1 fill:#2563eb,stroke:#1e40af,color:#fff
    classDef mode2 fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#5b21b6,color:#fff
    classDef agent fill:#059669,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#dc2626,stroke:#991b1b,color:#fff
    classDef infra fill:#475569,stroke:#334155,color:#fff

    class DD,Input1,Scrape1,Explain,Sections,Chat mode1
    class TM,Input2,KG,SR mode2
    class Diag,Disc,Graph,Scrape2,QuizGen agent
    class Home,CQ decision
    class Qdrant,SSE,Export infra
